//sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/kss/index.html?18,187 target=_blank rel=noopener>KATHĀS. 18,187.</a> отправляться в путь так <span class=ab>v. a.</span> умирать<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagavadgita/app1?8,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHAG. 8,5.</a> <i class=sa>prayāta</i> умерший<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagavadgita/app1?8,23 target=_blank rel=noopener>23.</a> протекать, проходить: <i class=sa>prayātāḥ sapta vāsarāḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/kss/index.html?4,23 target=_blank rel=noopener>KATHĀS. 4,23.</a> проходить, исчезать; о болезнях<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/Oxf_Cat_Aufrecht/index.html?234 target=_blank rel=noopener>Verz. d. Oxf. H. 234,b,5.</a> <i class=sa>lalāṭalekhā na punaḥ prayāti</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/boesp1/app1/?4948 target=_blank rel=noopener>Spr. 4948.</a><br><span class=ls>BĀLAB. 17.</span> разлетаться в разные стороны: <i class=sa>yathā prayānti saṃyānti srotovegena vālukāḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/boesp1/app1/?4787 target=_blank rel=noopener>Spr. 4787.</a> <i class=sa>truṭattantukaṃ muktājālamiva prayāti jhaṭiti bhraśyaddiśaḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/boesp1/app1/?3003 target=_blank rel=noopener>3003.</a>", "en_html": "— <i class=sa>pra</i><br> 1) to set out, to depart, to start on a journey; to go to —, to betake oneself to —, to travel/drive to (<span class=ab>acc.</span>): <i class=sa>pra ye yayuravṛkāso rathā iva</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.074.html#rv07.074.06 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 7,74,6.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.092.html#rv07.092.03 target=_blank rel=noopener>92,3.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.095.html#rv07.095.01 ta